# Hotel Management API вЂ“ Postman Documentation

# 1. Project Overview

The Hotel Management API Postman workspace was created to simplify the development, testing, and documentation of the Hotel Management backend services. The collection contains all endpoints required for user authentication, hotel management, room management, and file uploads. Postman was used not only for sending HTTP requests, but also for organizing the API, managing authentication, automating testing, and exploring advanced API development features.

---

# 2. Workspace Structure

A dedicated Postman workspace was created for the Hotel Management API project. Using a separate workspace keeps all project resources in one place and makes collaboration easier.

The workspace contains:

* Hotel Management API Collection
* Environment variables
* Request history
* API documentation
* Testing scripts

Keeping everything inside a single workspace improves project organization and allows future team members to quickly understand the API structure.

